# Cloud UAV ESM Plugin

README：[cloud/uav/README.md](../../cloud/uav/README.md)。Skill：`.cursor/skills/cloud-uav-esm-plugin/`。

## 与 map-plugin 区分

| | Map Tool | Cloud UAV |
| --- | --- | --- |
| 宿主 | saas-web | yunyan-web Vue |
| 集成 | map-plugin-bridge | `import()` + mount/unmount |

## 要点

- 公共 API：`mount(container)` / `unmount(container)`
- 新模块：`module-manifest.ts` + `src/modules/<id>/`
- **不用** `@vitejs/plugin-react`（`esbuild.jsx: automatic`）
- Drawer：用 `DrawerCloseButton`，避免 `DrawerClose asChild` + nested Button
- 路由离开 **`onBeforeUnmount`** 必须 `unmount`

```bash
pnpm --filter @repo/cloud-uav dev
pnpm --filter @repo/cloud-uav build
```
